Package: twisteR
Title: Play the Party Game Twister Even When You Don't Have the Game Essentials at Hand.
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Julia", "Strasheim", , "julia.strasheim@giga-hamburg.de",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
           person("David", "BenÄek", email = "david.bencek@ifw-kiel.de",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package to play the party game Twister without the spinner or the game mat.
    All you need is a common understanding of all players, where the four colours - red, green,
    blue and yellow - are located on the floor. A rug might help. The package then provides you
    with the play instructions so you can start placing your limbs.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: ggplot2
